ldren)</a></div><div id="display_t1_2jop" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_2jop" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Kazuo_Thow/">Kazuo_Thow</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">01 September 2010 03:38:48PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_2jop'>8 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_2jop'] = ['7 points', '8 points', '9 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_2jop')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_2jop" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
